1623			Long: `Inspect and clear the work cooldown that parks a bead from
1624	re-execution. Cooldowns are set automatically by the loop in three cases:
1625	
1626	  * no_changes with a vague rationale (short retry, default 6h)
1627	  * push_failed (long park, 365d, requires operator action)
1628	  * declined_needs_decomposition (long park, 365d, requires decomposition)
1629	
1630	Use this command instead of editing the magic Extra key directly:
1631	
1632	  ddx bead cooldown show <bead-id>     # show retry-after, last-status, last-detail
1633	  ddx bead cooldown clear <bead-id>    # remove cooldown so the bead re-enters the queue
